item.title: Captain Suite
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Spread out in style in our spacious One Bedroom Captain Suite. Well-appointed with modern, nautical-inspired decor and luxurious amenities, our suites are the height of refinement and style.
A spacious and well designed suite with balcony facing the forest and garden
The suite is well-designed and well furnished, the bedroom and living room are not separated. In the living room includes: sitting area, desk, coffee table and a 'Nespresso' coffee maker. The bedroom includes: an 'Aminach Forest Mattress' which was designed especially for the resort, reading lamps and a closet. The suite also includes a grand bathroom.
The suite opens to a sun balcony with 2 patio lounge chairs, viewing the garden. There are Planters on both sides of the balcony.
Suite guests can watch free DVDs, all you need to do is choosing your favorite films from our collection (at the front desk).

item.title: Three Bedroom Apartment
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Our three bedroom, two bathroom apartments are perfect for family or corporate groups coming to London.
These apartments are very spacious and exceptionally decorated. You can opt for king size doubles or twin beds as well as an additional sofa bed in the lounge (£30/night surcharge).
They sleep a maximum of seven adults or six adults and two children and have all the modern amenities you need, including a fridge, toaster and microwave, satellite TV and a DVD library and complementary tea, coffee and milk every day.
Enjoy additional space and views of the harbor below in our Harbor Corner King room featuring an array of luxurious amenities and vibrant contemporary design.
A spacious and well designed suite with balcony facing the forest and garden
The suite is well-designed and well furnished, the bedroom and living room are not separated. In the living room includes: sitting area, desk, coffee table and a 'Nespresso' coffee maker. The bedroom includes: an 'Aminach Forest Mattress' which was designed especially for the resort, reading lamps and a closet. The suite also includes a grand bathroom.
The suite opens to a sun balcony with 2 patio lounge chairs, viewing the garden. There are Planters on both sides of the balcony.
Suite guests can watch free DVDs, all you need to do is choosing your favorite films from our collection (at the front desk).

item.title: Two Bedroom Duplex Apartment
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Each of our two bedroom, one bathroom apartments are very comfortably furnished and sleeps either five adults or four adults and two children.
The bedrooms have a choice of King size double or twin beds, there’s a very spacious lounge and dining area with a sofa bed (£30/night surcharge) and a fully equipped kitchen with all the amenities you need for a comfortable stay.
Perfect for entertaining, relaxing and using as a great base from where to explore London.
Choose either our Mountain Terrace Room offering scenic views of the nearby mountains or the Marina Terrace Room overlooking the marina. Each of our Terrace Rooms are well-appointed with luxurious amenities and modern decor inspired by the Rodney Bay's maritime heritage.

Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)

...or something like this:

The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.

As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!
